{"tid":1417410,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"求下你地，轉戰機場","createTime":"2019-08-05T16:32:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T08:51:21.000Z","uid":16406,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"aaa12e12abf9017f83da3acd6257eb186c08b400","tid":1417410,"uid":16406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T16:32:24.000Z","msg":"雖然我知我係執緊人口水尾<br />\n但唔該 可唔可以轉戰機場 有咩好處好多人講過 唔多講了<br />\n<br />\n今日 咁多手足都沖左出黎同時佔左咁多區 食左咁多蛋<br />\n班狗雖然稱唔上游刃有餘 但都叫做應付到<br />\n當咁多區同時佔班狗都唔打柴<br />\n同時又有咁多兄弟比人拉<br />\n<br />\n我地係時候要變陣去機場<br />\n揸住正苦個春袋<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">義士真係少一個就少一個 義士被拉真係好心痛</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n想同咁多位講聲 民意方面我地無輸到<br />\n發夢果陣見到有好多街坊幫我地指路 問我地要唔要口罩 小心啲 加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f519aa30466233757338afe3228ed7af2f81c98e","tid":1417410,"uid":16406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T16:35:14.000Z","msg":"我無野講"},{"pid":"ccdb1f96e5192a22e576e663789ab82d37948a36","tid":1417410,"uid":16406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T16:35:25.000Z","msg":"我無野講"},{"pid":"61010220632a50620719dbec4e8ee6094fa1ce06","tid":1417410,"uid":16406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T16:36:16.000Z","msg":"我無野講"},{"pid":"c147198dbcad34260e72f92b13e9797f1a256ff3","tid":1417410,"uid":262091,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f519aa30466233757338afe3228ed7af2f81c98e","tid":1417410,"uid":16406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T16:35:14.000Z","msg